<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><hymn_number>319</hymn_number>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1. Dettak in ding un, khawvel buoina ah,
 Huihpi nungin, tuikinawk sang mahleh;
 Zie Suongpi hin hatna, hinna ei piei,
 Gitlohna a hung naih tieng.

[V2]
 Suongpi chunga dingin! dettak in ding hitiu!
 Krista Suongpi chung ngeiah;
 I do ham ham chun bittak in ding hitiu,
 Lalchutphah vel mipi lakah.

[V3]
 2. Thudik ah dingdet un, lunggil thieng pu'n,
 Lunggil dik, hangsan leh ginna hatin;
 Zie Suongpi mai hin zawhna ei piena,
 Khawvel gitlohna lakah.

[V4]
 3. Thudik ah dingdet un, nang di'n phapen,
 Ahun sawt mahleh, hung tung tei ina;
 Suongpi hin chawlhna, muonna ei piena,
 Damsung huihpi a beih tieng.</lyrics>
<title>FIRMLY STAND!</title>
</song>